{
  "Changes": [
    {
      "LogName": "Hogwarts Mail Letter Data",
      "Action": "EditData",
      "Target": "Data/Mail",
      "Entries": {
        "{{ModId}}_HogwartsLetter": "HOGWARTS SCHOOL of WITCHCRAFT and WIZARDRY^HEADMISTRESS: Professor Minerva McGonagall^(Order of Merlin, First Class)^Dear ${Mr^Ms}$ @^We are pleased to inform you that you have successfully passed your first year at Hogwarts. Enclosed is your report and a list of necessary books and equipment for the upcoming year.^Place the emblem attached to the letter at one of the designated spots for an owl to pick up.^The new school year shall begin soon; we look forward to your owl's reply.^Sincerely,^Filius Flitwick^Deputy Headmaster^COURSE BOOKS^All students should have a copy of each of the following:^Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them^by Newt Scamander^The Monster Book of Monsters^by Edwardus Lima^OTHER EQUIPMENT^1 wand^1 cauldron^1 telescope^1 dark detector with eyes^Students may also bring, if they desire, a pet.^Yours sincerely,^Lucinda Thomsonicle-Pocus^Chief Attendant of Witchcraft Provisions^%item object 388 1 %%[#]A Letter From Hogwarts"
      }
    },
    {
